{"_id":"4wsTErlbtttYTonx","name":"Command Undead","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Classes/passive/necromancer_012.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Command_Undead\" class=\"mw-headline\">Command Undead</span></h2>\n<p>Starting at 14th level, you can use magic to bring undead under your control, even those created by other necromancers. As an action, you can choose one undead that you can see within 60 feet of you. That creature must make a Personality saving throw against your necromancer spell save DC. If it succeeds, you can't use this feature on it again. If it fails, it becomes friendly to you and obeys your commands until you use this feature again. </p>\n<p>Intelligent undead are harder to control in this way. If the target has an Intelligence of 8 or higher, it has advantage on the saving throw. If it fails the saving throw and has an Intelligence of 12 or higher, it can repeat the saving throw at the end of every hour until it succeeds and breaks free.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enemies of Elsweyr pg 10","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"Only works on undead"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":1,"width":null,"units":"","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":60,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"cha","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Baleful Summoner 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_jc2f383nlwg","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Necromancer Feats#/CF_SEP/Baleful Summoner","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"5Fq6EyfY6nQDPj1s","name":"Performer's Vainglory","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/melee/sword-winged-holy-orange.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Performer.27s_Vainglory\" class=\"mw-headline\">Performer's Vainglory</span></h2>\n<p>At 3rd level, you become invigorated when you witness someone being inspired by your own performances. When at least one creature you have inspired with your Bardic Inspiration is within 30 feet of you and they still have their Bardic Inspiration die, you gain a bonus to your attacks. When your attack hits a target, roll a die equal to your Bardic Inspiration die and add that number to the attacks damage roll.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Basic Rules v1.4 pg 38","activation":{"type":"none","cost":null,"condition":"When at least one creature you have inspired with your Bardic Inspiration is within 30 feet of you and they still have their Bardic Inspiration die"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"College of Reveries 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"yEObuQw8ZcySokFv","changes":[{"key":"flags.midi-qol.optional.NAME.attack","mode":2,"value":"1d(2*floor((classes.bard.levels+5)/5)+4)","priority":"20"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"rounds":1,"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/skills/melee/sword-winged-holy-orange.webp","label":"Vainglory","origin":"Item.5Fq6EyfY6nQDPj1s","transfer":true,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":true}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":"flags.midi-qol.optional.NAME.attack"}