{"_id":"DV8DOuuV0MUsRNbl","name":"Elemental Mastery: Cryomancer","type":"feat","img":"UESTRPG/Icons/Weapon/Destro/ON-icon-skill-Destruction_Staff-Ice_Storm.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Elemental_Mastery\" class=\"mw-headline\">Elemental Mastery</span></h2>\n<p>At level 2, you choose one type of element to have exceptional power over.</p>\n<h3><span id=\"Cryomancer\" class=\"mw-headline\">Cryomancer</span></h3>\n<p>You prefer the cold of elemental frost, freezing your enemies in their tracks. Whenever a creature takes cold damage from a spell that you cast, the target's speed is also reduced by 15 feet until the end of your next turn. If the spell already reduces the target's speed, use whichever reduction is greater.</p>\n<p>When you reach 11th level, you reduce the target's speed by 20 feet.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 117","activation":{"type":"none","cost":0,"condition":"Whenever a creature takes cold damage from a spell that you cast"},"duration":{"value":1,"units":"turn"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"School of Destruction 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"yGjZktu2XxRcHgtb","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.walk","mode":2,"value":"-15","priority":"25"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"rounds":1,"startTime":null},"icon":"UESTRPG/Icons/Weapon/Destro/ON-icon-skill-Destruction_Staff-Ice_Storm.png","label":"Elemental Mastery: Cryomancer","origin":"Item.DV8DOuuV0MUsRNbl","transfer":true,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":true}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":"data.attributes.movement.walk"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_w04ihw3ubv","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Mage Feats#/CF_SEP/Destruction","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"DYFXZX9mUWWdyo3z","name":"Relentless Rage","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Classes/passive/dragonknight_024.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Relentless_Rage\" class=\"mw-headline\">Relentless Rage</span></h2>\n<p>Starting at 11th level, your rage can keep you fighting despite grievous wounds. If you drop to 0 hit points while you’re raging and don’t die outright, you can make a DC 10 Endurance saving throw. If you succeed, you drop to 1 hit point instead. Each time you use this feature after the first, the DC increases by 5. When you finish a short or long rest, the DC resets to 10.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Basic Rules v1.4 pg 30","activation":{"type":"special","cost":null,"condition":"If you drop to 0 hit points while you're raging and don't die outright"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":1,"max":"1","per":"lr","type":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1","healing"]],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":10,"scaling":"flat","value":""},"requirements":"Barbarian 11","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.FqfmbPgxiyrWzhYk"},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_xgt9dlxpc7","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Barbarian Feats","color":"#000000","sort":900000}}}
