{"_id":"MocK59g1plFUckiN","name":"Plague Spreader","type":"feat","img":"UESTRPG/Icons/Classes/Necromancer/Grave%20Death/ON-icon-skill-Grave_Lord-Detonating_Siphon.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Plague_Spreader\" class=\"mw-headline\">Plague Spreader</span></h2>\n<p>At 18th level, you can expend one or more Soul Points and use an action to choose a corpse you can see or a creature infected by a disease. The corpse or creature explodes in a burst of disease, forcing each creature within 10 feet of it to make an Endurance saving throw. On a failed save, each creature takes 2d8 necrotic damage for each Soul Point expended and they are infected with the same disease the creature was infected with. If the target is a corpse, you can choose to spread a disease that you know. A creature takes half as much damage on a successful save and is not infected by the disease.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"EoE pg. 15","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":10,"long":null,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":1},"ability":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d8","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"con","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Undying Warrior 18","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_a1cuhktmv3t","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Necromancer Feats#/CF_SEP/Deathbringer","color":"#000000"}}}
