{"_id":"kK1Dw2aw4rus1LNl","name":"Art Spells","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Classes/necromancer/003_b.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Art_Spells\" class=\"mw-headline\">Art Spells</span></h2>\n<p><em>2nd-level Corpse Whisper feature</em><br /><br />Your necromantic art grants you the ability to cast certain spells. At 3rd, 5th, 7th, and 9th level you gain access to arts spells. See the Art Spells class feature in <a title=\"EoE:Necromancer\" href=\"https://wiki.uestrpg.com/wiki/EoE:Necromancer\"><em>Enemies of Elsweyr</em></a> for how art spells work.</p>\n<table class=\"uestrpgtable\"><caption>Corpse Whisperer Art Spells</caption>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Level</th>\n<th>Spells</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td><a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/see-invisibility\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/see-invisibility\"><em>see invisibility</em></a>, <a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/zone-of-truth\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/zone-of-truth\"><em>zone of truth</em></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td><a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/clairvoyance\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/clairvoyance\"><em>clairvoyance</em></a>, <a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/tongues\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/tongues\"><em>tongues</em></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td><a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/divination\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/divination\"><em>divination</em></a>, <a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/locate creature\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/locate_creature\"><em>locate creature</em></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td><a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/hallow,\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/hallow,\"><em>hallow,</em></a>, <a class=\"extiw\" title=\"dndbeyond:spells/scrying\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/spells/scrying\"><em>scrying</em></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Enemies of Elsweyr pg 10","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Corpse Whisperer 2","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_x9lzmvjp5z","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Necromancer Feats#/CF_SEP/Corpse Whisperer","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"kltlCpRXxN00pw8H","name":"Illuminating Spirit","type":"feat","img":"UESTRPG/Icons/Classes/Templar/Dawns%20Wrath/ON-icon-skill-Dawn%27s_Wrath-Unstable_Core.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><em><strong>Illuminating Spirit.</strong></em> As an action, you use your Channel Divinity to cause light to shine down on you, restoring a number of magicka points equal to half your Crusader level, rounded down.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Basic Rules v1.4 pg 47","activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":"self"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":"self"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Templar 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"ttICWgfHddMShHVC","changes":[{"key":"data.resources.primary.value","mode":2,"value":"@classes.crusader.levels / 2","priority":"20"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"turns":1},"icon":"UESTRPG/Icons/Classes/Templar/Dawns%20Wrath/ON-icon-skill-Dawn%27s_Wrath-Unstable_Core.png","label":"Illuminating Spirit","origin":"Item.kltlCpRXxN00pw8H","transfer":true,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":true}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":"data.resources.primary.value"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_r9nvdchcf0i","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Crusader Feats#/CF_SEP/Templar","color":"#000000"}}}
{"_id":"kuQt830L2MJcQrha","name":"Deflect Missiles","type":"feat","img":"icons/skills/ranged/arrow-flying-white-blue.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<h3><span id=\"Deflect_Missiles\" class=\"mw-headline\">Deflect Missiles</span></h3>\n<p>Starting at 3rd level, you can use your reaction to deflect or catch the missile when you are hit by a ranged weapon attack. When you do so, the damage you take from the attack is reduced by 1d10 + your Agility modifier + your monk level.</p>\n<p>If you reduce the damage to 0, you can catch the missile if it is small enough for you to hold in one hand and you have at least one hand free. If you catch a missile in this way, you can spend 1 stamina point to make a ranged attack with the weapon or piece of ammunition you just caught, as part of the same reaction. You make this attack with proficiency, regardless of your weapon proficiencies, and the missile deals damage equal to your unarmed strike, which has a normal range of 20 feet and a long range of 60 feet.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PHB pg. 78","activation":{"type":"reaction","cost":1,"condition":"Can be thrown back using 1 ki point"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":20,"long":60,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":0,"max":"0","per":"","type":""},"consume":{"type":"attribute","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":"0","chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d4 + @mod",""]],"versatile":"","value":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell","value":""},"requirements":"Monk 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"Bpht1hPRQraOwtWN","changes":[{"key":"flags.midi-qol.DR.piercing","mode":0,"value":"1d10 + @abilities.dex.mod + @classes.monk.levels","priority":"20"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"icons/skills/ranged/arrow-strike-apple-orange.webp","label":"Catch Missile","origin":"Item.kuQt830L2MJcQrha","transfer":true,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":true}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":"flags.midi-qol.DR.piercing"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.dnd5e.classfeatures.mzweVbnsJPQiVkAe"},"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"cf":{"id":"temp_y8r2zjxypvj","path":"Class Features#/CF_SEP/Monk Feats","color":"#000000"}}}
