{"name":"Hunt-Father's Advance","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Guild/fightersguild/004_a.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Hunt-Father.27s_Advance\" class=\"mw-headline\">Hunt-Father's Advance</span></h2>\n<p><em>6th-level Path of the Wilds feature</em><br /><br />When you or an ally within 10 feet of you attacks and hits a creature that is surprised, the target takes an additional 1d4 damage. This damage increases when you reach certain levels: to 2d4 at 11th level, 3d4 at 16th level, and 4d4 at 20th level. The bonus damage depends on the damage type of the weapon or spell being used.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LGtC pg 13","activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":"inst"},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"any","type":"creature"},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":""},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"other","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["floor(@details.level - 1 / 5)d4",""]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Path of the Wilds 6","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"midi-qol":{"effectActivation":false},"core":{"sourceId":"Item.N5K0MiKd2flRubH4"}},"_id":"U9OjH2Jgv867rQtr"}
{"name":"Primal Cunning","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Guild/fightersguild/005_b.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Primal_Cunning\" class=\"mw-headline\">Primal Cunning</span></h2>\n<p><em>3rd-level Path of the Wilds feature</em><br /><br />You have an unmatched connection to the natural environment. You become proficient in one skill of your choice from Animal Handling, Nature, Medicine, Perception, Stealth, or Survival. While in a natural environment, your proficiency bonus is doubled for any attribute check you make that uses this chosen skill.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LGtC pg 13","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Path of the Wilds 3","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"Xkvwazu772cFZOId","changes":[{"key":"data.skills.ani.value","mode":5,"value":"1","priority":"20"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Guild/fightersguild/005_b.png","label":"Bonus Proficiency","origin":"Item.AJwUPUKAWIjo4AHR","transfer":true,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","durationExpression":"","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":true}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":"data.skills.ani.value"}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.AJwUPUKAWIjo4AHR"}},"_id":"KH0z8GE2g8bGKDOs"}
{"name":"Resilient Rage","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Classes/dragonknight/016a.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Resilient_Rage\" class=\"mw-headline\">Resilient Rage</span></h2>\n<p><em>14th-level Path of the Wilds feature</em><br /><br />While raging, you are immune to the charmed and frightened condition and you have advantage on saving throws against being blinded, deafened, paralyzed, petrified, poisoned, or stunned.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LGtC pg 13","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Path of the Wilds 14","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"edXPS9wugMKG2ynx","changes":[{"key":"data.traits.ci.value","mode":2,"value":"charmed","priority":"20"},{"key":"data.traits.ci.value","mode":2,"value":"frightened","priority":"20"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"rounds":10,"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Classes/dragonknight/016a.png","label":"Resilient Rage","origin":"Item.uRPjGF1yeA7WKDQf","transfer":false,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","durationExpression":"","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":false}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":["data.traits.ci.value","data.traits.ci.value"]}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.uRPjGF1yeA7WKDQf"}},"_id":"kxDA5dBhSwynyRQB"}
{"name":"Silent Strider","type":"feat","img":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Guild/fightersguild/002_a.png","data":{"description":{"value":"<h2><span id=\"Silent_Strider\" class=\"mw-headline\">Silent Strider</span></h2>\n<p><em>10th-level Path of the Wilds feature</em><br /><br />Your walking speed increases by 5 feet and you gain your choice of either a climbing speed or a swimming speed, which equals your walking speed. <br /><br />Additionally, you have advantage on an Agility (Stealth) check if you move no more than half your speed on the same turn.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"LGtC pg 13","activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":"","per":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":null,"actionType":"","attackBonus":0,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"requirements":"Path of the Wilds 10","recharge":{"value":null,"charged":false}},"effects":[{"_id":"5FsOXDHK3ZLx79OY","changes":[{"key":"data.attributes.movement.walk","mode":2,"value":"5","priority":"20"},{"key":"data.attributes.movement.climb","mode":5,"value":"@attributes.movement.walk","priority":"15"}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null},"icon":"modules/uestrpg5e/artwork/ESO/ability/Guild/fightersguild/002_a.png","label":"Silent Strider","origin":"Item.JjdJjqmhDUfqEkSt","transfer":true,"flags":{"core":{"statusId":""},"dae":{"stackable":"none","durationExpression":"","macroRepeat":"none","specialDuration":[],"transfer":true}},"tint":null,"selectedKey":["data.attributes.movement.walk","data.attributes.movement.climb"]}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"7p78eooyEyF8LXNq":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.JjdJjqmhDUfqEkSt"}},"_id":"A9RpCr3uTlUqD